      "Systematic survey of 88 primary studies on job recommender systems published from 2011 to 2025, spanning classical keyword matching to LLM, retrieval-augmented, and agentic architectures.",
      "No model applied by the authors; the paper builds the four-dimensional RMKO taxonomy and codes studies using multidimensional coding, Spearman correlations, and Hamming-distance clustering.",
      "Identifies four architectural archetypes converging toward interactive or agentic generative systems, with persistent asymmetries in knowledge grounding and output sophistication across the reviewed literature."
